comments.content:
Looks like a custom job based on [Dekar](http://web.archive.org/web/20131014183534/http:/fontfabric.com/dekar-free-font) to me, "just" need to remove some parts from /a, /r and /b vertical stems.  
If you need a confirmation, try asking [Eduardo Mateos](http://web.archive.org/web/20131014183534/http:/www.behance.net/gallery/Clinica-Corbal-Branding/2304182).
Yes, very similar. Thanks once more RYUK!
